        -----------
        Development
        -----------
        
        #. Clone the repo
            .. code-block:: text
        
                git clone https://github.com/hananf11/flask_image_search.git
        #. move into the folder
            ``cd ./flask_image_search``
        #. pip install with dev requirements
            .. code-block:: text
        
                pip3 install .[dev]
